{"tid":1918859,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"復刻 PC Engine 迷你版   因疫情緣故需要延期上市","createTime":"2020-03-10T11:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T10:44:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"148ec745612eb1daa169d817abf62bed893f3b5c","tid":1918859,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:11:55.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎除了奪去人們性命，亦對各行各業造成打擊，大陸不少工廠和辦公室都因此需要關閉，就連遊戲公司 Konami 亦受到牽連。他們昨日透過官方 Twitter 帳號宣佈，由於武漢肺炎疫情的緣故，導致他們的復刻版遊戲主機需要延期推出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKonami 原本打算在 3 月 19 日將迷你復刻版 PC Engine 的日本、歐洲和北美機型上市，但現在卻需要延期。根據 Konami 歐洲的官方聲明，生產上述迷你主機和配件的大陸工廠，還有物流設施都受到武漢肺炎疫情影響而需要暫停運作，導致新機的上市日期需要押後，直到另行通知。<br />\n<br />\nPC Engine 因應日本、歐洲和北美市場，分別以 PC Engine、PC Engine Core Grafx 和 TurboGrafx-16 名義上市；Konami 在生產復刻版時亦依照上述 3 款主機不同設計，推出對應的迷你版。Konami 在聲明中向受影響的顧客致歉，又表示會盡力將遊戲主機盡快推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/10/konami-turbografx-16-mini-delayed-until-further-notice-due-to-covid-19/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F10%2Fkonami-turbografx-16-mini-delayed-until-further-notice-due-to-covid-19%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eStgc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=dd8ef10b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/10/konami-turbografx-16-mini-delayed-until-further-notice-due-to-covid-19/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"fa454a0e1f6877100f664da85cbe173a47b92856","tid":1918859,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"老貓會唔會買黎玩"},{"pid":"9d77f44d0b2477ed4000c1699f436c6e019de622","tid":1918859,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa454a0e1f6877100f664da85cbe173a47b92856","tid":1918859,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"老貓會唔會買黎玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"無限delay"},{"pid":"a5ab25de80b6b0c339049ad7355f974df3cb2e3f","tid":1918859,"uid":174692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"Fuck u Konami"}]}